</a>
</section>
</div>
<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p>随着开学季的到来，学生们陆续返校，学校食堂也逐渐成为了这一宣传的重要阵地。</p>
<p>虽然现在“光盘行动”和“节约粮食”的理念渐渐被大家接受，勤俭节约的风气也逐渐形成，但还是有一些地方餐饮浪费行为仍然存在。</p>
<p>也希望同学们在日常生活中要爱惜粮食，一起加入“光盘行动”的队伍当中来，一起杜绝“舌尖上的浪费”。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200914/d896a76b64f64480a57a821987251517.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>下面为大家总结了一些节约粮食相关的英文句子，一起来看看吧！</p>
<p>1.Save Food And Eat Healthily</p>
<p>节约粮食，健康饮食</p>
<p>2.Pearl is treasure, rice is king.</p>
<p>珍珠为宝，稻米为王。</p>
<p>3.Behold dishes, each all pain.</p>
<p>谁知盘中餐，粒粒皆辛苦。</p>
<p>4.practicing thrift and opposing waste.</p>
<p>厉行节约、反对浪费</p>
<p>5.Advocate festival food culture, and promote the sustainable development.</p>
<p>崇尚节粮风气，促进可持续发展。</p>
<p>6.Save food, starts from me, starts from now!</p>
<p>节约粮食，从我做起，从现在做起！</p>
<p>7.Never forget to be hungry when you are full!</p>
<p>饱时不忘饿时饥！</p>
<p>8.Cherish food, away from waste.</p>
<p>珍惜粮食，远离浪费。</p>
<p>9.Enhance saving food, sparing the consciousness of food.</p>
<p>增强节约粮食，爱惜粮食的意识。</p>
<p>10.Treasure grain, saving food.</p>
<p>爱惜粮食，节约粮食。</p>
<p>11.Treasure grain, everyone duty!</p>
<p>爱惜粮食，人人有责！</p>
<p>12.Save grain starts from me and build a conservation-minded society.</p>
<p>节粮从我做起，建设节约型社会。</p>
<p>13.It is shameful to waste food.</p>
<p>浪费粮食是可耻的。</p>
<p>14.Cherish food is to love life.</p>
<p>珍惜粮食就是热爱生命。</p>
<p>15.Save food glorious, shame on waste food.</p>
<p>节约粮食光荣，浪费粮食可耻。</p>
<p>16.A porridge a meal when the hard-won, silk half wisp of constant reading material.</p>
<p>一粥一饭当思来之不易，半丝半缕恒念物力维艰。</p>
<p>17、节约从粮食开始。</p>
<p>Save from food.</p>
<p>18.Cherish food, get in the habit to save.</p>
<p>珍惜粮食，养成节约好习惯。</p>
<p>19.Drinking water to ses, dinner when frugality. Each block and are hard to change.</p>
<p>饮水要思源，吃饭当节俭。粒粒盘中餐，皆是辛苦换。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200914/a6b249c84032484ab79c9c63d2886f3f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>20.Oppose wasting food.</p>
<p>反对浪费粮食。</p>
<p>21.Food is the essence of the people.</p>
<p>民以食为天。</p>
<p>22.It is a virtue to cherish food.</p>
<p>珍惜粮食是一种美德。</p>
<p>23.Along with the advance of the society, more and more problems are brought to our attention, one of which is wasting food.</p>
<p>随着社会的发展，越来越多的问题引起了我们的注意，其中一个就是浪费食物。</p>
<p>24.Wasting food is not only an immoral behavior, but also pollutes the environment.</p>
<p>浪费食物不仅是一种不道德的行为，而且还会污染环境。</p>
<p>25.We can start from small things, such as, don't order more food than we can eat, eat up all the food in the bowls and so on.</p>
<p>我们可以从小事做起，例如，不点多于我们食量的食物，吃完碗里的食物等等。</p>
<p>26.At the same time, we shouldn't eat junk food but healthy food.</p>
<p>同时，我们也不应该吃垃圾食品而是应该吃健康的食物。</p>
<p>27.It's good for our health to have a balanced diet.</p>
<p>保持饮食平衡对我们的健康是很有益的。</p>
<p>28.In order to our healthy body, we had better eat in school or at home as soon as possible.</p>
<p>为了我们的身体健康，我们最好尽量在学校或者家里吃。</p>
<p>29.It is necessary to further enhance public awareness of the issue, effectively cultivate thrifty habits and foster a social environment where waste is shameful and thriftiness is applaudable.</p>
<p>要进一步加强宣传教育，切实培养节约习惯，在全社会营造浪费可耻、节约为荣的氛围。</p>
<p>30.A recent survey has shown that 91.2% of the Chinese respondents tend to take home their leftovers when dining out.</p>
<p>近日的一项调查显示，91.2%的国内受访者外出就餐时有打包剩菜的习惯。</p>
<p>31.Around 92% of the respondents believed saving food is a virtue that would never become anachronic, and 85.7% said saving food squares with the contemporary concept that values the quality of life, according to the survey conducted by China Youth Daily.</p>
<p>由《中国青年报》实施的这项调查显示，约92%的受访者认为节约粮食是永不过时的美德，85.7%的受访者认为，节约粮食与当下品质生活理念相契合。</p>
<p>32.Around 61.8% advised restaurants and eateries to offer serving chopsticks, which would be instrumental for customers to pack the leftovers.</p>
<p>约61.8%的受访者建议餐馆提供公筷，方便人们将剩菜打包。</p>
<p>33.A similar proportion of respondents said it might be useful to promote smaller-portion or half-portion dishes.</p>
<p>同等比例的受访者称，推广小份菜、半例菜可能是节约粮食的有用途径。</p>
<p>34.About 59% advised catering businesses to introduce coupons or other incentives for customers who clear their plates after dinner.</p>
<p>约59%的受访者建议餐饮企业对"光盘"的消费者提供代金券等奖励。</p>
<p>35.Establish the awareness of saving grain and cherish the fruits of labor.</p>
<p>树立节粮意识，珍惜劳动成果。</p>
<p>粮食是不可以浪费的，每一粒粮食都来之不易，都是经过了播种、耕种到收割及一些列的其他工序，才走上餐桌的，与此同时，还有很多人吃不饱饭，不要以为你吃饱了，就可以随便浪费。</p>
<p>节约粮食，从现在做起，从我做起，让每个人都能吃上饭，吃饱饭。</p>